"Next, enter a :guilabel:`Track Date` and time for the track, and designate "
"a :guilabel:`Location` where the talk is planning to be held."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_tracks.rst:108
msgid ""
"To access a complete list of locations for event tracks, which can be "
"modified (and added to) at any time, navigate to :menuselection:`Events app "
"--> Configuration --> Track Locations`."
msgstr ""
"For at få adgang til en komplet liste over placeringer til arrangementspor, "
"som kan ændres (og tilføjes til) når som helst, skal du navigere til "
":menuselection:`Arrangementer-app --> Konfiguration --> Sporplaceringer`."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_tracks.rst:111
msgid "Then, add a :guilabel:`Duration` to the track (in minutes)."
