#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_tracks.rst:122
msgid ""
"Then, ensure the track is applied to the correct event in "
"the :guilabel:`Event` field. By default, this field is auto-populated with "
"the event related to the *Event Tracks* page the track was originally "
